The paper describes a case study of providing a content management system for maintaining and updating high volume of content in various forms like text, data, audio, video etc and providing a facility for user to access from anywhere using mobile devices. The application requires a cross platform application development environment and the paper describes the experience and challenges in developing the application. This application was developed in collaboration with National Informatics Center (NIC), to explore the feasibility of this approach and technologies for e-Governance applications. (6 pages)